  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nWhen user has `Appearance` -> `Show profile pictures of` -> `Everyone` and `Accept new chats from` -> `Anyone` chat requests which appears in `Activity Center` does not have custom user image if it was set. But it appears right away when open chat view. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nCustom user icon is visible on the Activity Center view\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/115217372-1b9fbe80-a10e-11eb-8e0a-b99eacac4204.mov\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Create two new users: UserA and UserB\r\n- UserA enables `Profile` -> `Appearance` -> `Show profile pictures of `-> `Everyone` setting\r\n- UserB sets custom profile image\r\n- UserB sends text message to UserA\r\n- UserA opes Activity Center where UserB's request is visible\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: develop 1.12\r\n- Operating System: Android and iOS",
